6 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Transfer of funds. The state treasurer shall transfer:
7 (1) $50 million from the general fund to the Montana water development state special revenue
8 account established in [section 1] by [30 days after the effective date of this act];
9 (1)(2) $50 million from the general fund to the Montana water development state special revenue
10 account established in [section 1] by August 1, 2025; and
11 (2)(3) $50 million from the general fund to the Montana water development state special revenue
12 account established in [section 1] by August 1, 2026.
